    public class ST25TV64KTag
extends ST25TVHighDensityTag
    Provide implementation of ST25TV64KTag tags with access to main features as Password management, Areas configuration, NDEF related functions, Tag informations, Type5Tag commands and ST custom commands, CC file, System file.
